-- Erste Group picks Bravek as new COO 
-- By Michael Shields
-- Fri Dec 12, 2014 04:11AM EST
-- None



VIENNA, Dec 12 (Reuters) - Austrian lender Erste Group Bank <ERST.VI> has appointed Petr Bravek as chief operating officer as of April 1, replacing Herbert Juranek, who will resign from the management board at the end of this year, it said on Friday.

